OL,3,CSir Chris Hoy announces that his
OL,4,Ccancer is terminal
OL,6,FSir Chris Hoy, one of Britain's
OL,7,Fgreatest cyclists and Olympians, has
OL,8,Fannounced that his cancer is terminal.
OL,10,FHe was given a diagnosis last year
OL,11,Fthat he has two to four years left to
OL,12,Flive.
OL,14,FSir Chris, 48, told The Sunday Times:
OL,15,F"As unnatural as it feels, this is
OL,16,Fnature."
OL,18,FHe added: "You know, we were all born
OL,19,Fand we all die, and this is just part
OL,20,Fof the process.
