OL,6,FSome weeks before his cancer
OL,7,Fdiagnosis, his wife Sarra had tests on
OL,8,Fa tingling sensation in her face and
OL,9,Ftongue.
OL,11,FThen just before Christmas it was
OL,12,Fconfirmed she had multiple sclerosis
OL,13,F(MS) that was "very active and
OL,14,Faggressive" and needed urgent
OL,15,Ftreatment.
OL,17,FThe couple have not told their
OL,18,Fchildren about Sarra's MS diagnosis.
