OL,6,FHe was such a dominant force in sprint
OL,7,Fcycling that he had won six Olympic,
OL,8,F11 world and 34 World Cup titles by
OL,9,Fthe time he retired from competitive
OL,10,Fracing in 2013.
OL,12,FSir Chris has six Olympic gold medals
OL,13,Fand one silver ` only his former team-
OL,14,Fmate Sir Jason Kenny has won more
OL,15,FOlympic gold medals for Great Britain.
OL,17,FThe Scot, originally from Edinburgh,
OL,18,Fhad asked for privacy following the
OL,19,Fannouncement.
