OL,6,FHe was awarded his knighthood in 2008
OL,7,Fat the same time that his mother
OL,8,FCarol, a retired nurse, was recognised
OL,9,Fwith an MBE for her work on sleep-
OL,10,Frelated illnesses.
OL,12,FInspired to try cycling by a scene in
OL,13,Fthe film E.T., Hoy soon reached the
OL,14,Fworld's top 10 rankings in BMX and in
OL,15,Faddition was a medallist at the
OL,16,FScottish Junior Rowing Championships.
OL,18,FHis rise to the top mirrored his
OL,19,Fnation's emergence to the top of track
OL,20,Fcycling.
